description:
Applicability
This schedule applies to: 1) pumping of subsurface water for drainage or irrigation which is not eligible to be served with electricity sold to the District by the City and County of San Francisco pursuant to Section 9(l) of the Federal Raker Act; or 2) pumping from natural waterways or District facilities. This schedule is applicable on an annual basis only.
name: Schedule FX Farm Service - Irrigation Pumping Time-Of-Use
